title: Dual Olympic gold medallist Bayley into Sport Australia... (Australian Cycling Federation)
text: ( Source : Australian Cycling Federation ) West Australian Ryan Bayley will become the fifth cyclist to inducted as a Member of the Sport Australia Hall of Fame . Bayley, 33, will be inducted at the the 31st Sport Australia Hall of Fame
